flowchart LR
 subgraph Branches["🌿 Environment Promotion"]
        Dev["🌱 dev"]
        QA["🧪 qa"]
        Main["🚀 main"]
  end
    Dev --> QA
    QA --> Main
    DataRepo["📦 hydrosat-data<br>Builds and publishes runtime image"] -- Build and publish image --> DockerHub["🐳 Docker Hub<br>Stores published image"]
    DockerHub -- Image tag referenced in values --> InfraRepo["🏗️ hydrosat-infra<br>Terraform + GitOps configuration"]
    InfraRepo --> Branches
    Branches --> InfraCI["✅ Infra CI<br>Validate Terraform + config"] & InfraDelivery["🏗️ Infra Delivery<br>Apply Terraform + sync GitOps"]
    InfraDelivery -- After infra is healthy --> AlertRepo["🚨 alert-delivery<br>Grafana alert rules (Alert-as-Code)"]